00:04:50.275 --> 00:04:52.345
AR: Penge. Okay, lad os prøve med det.

00:04:52.345 --> 00:04:55.059
Kan du stå lige herovre for mig?

00:04:55.059 --> 00:04:56.457
Vend dig om og, lad os se,

00:04:56.457 --> 00:04:58.102
